name: Windows Gather Proxy Setting
author: mubix <mubix@hak5.org>
description:
This module pulls a user's proxy settings. If neither RHOST or SID
        are set it pulls the current user, else it will pull the user's settings
        specified SID and target host.

options.name: WORKSPACE
options.description: Specify the workspace for this module

options.name: SESSION
options.description: The session to run this module on.

options.name: RHOST
options.description: Remote host to clone settings to, defaults to local

options.name: SID
options.description: SID of user to clone settings to (SYSTEM is S-1-5-18)
